    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the Old Babylonian period from 1894 to 1595 BCE, during which one dynasty ruled parts of Mesopotamia. It included the reign of Hammurabi, considered the golden age of the Old Babylonian period.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Se refiere al período Babilónico Antiguo de 1894 a 1595 a.C., durante el cual la dinastía gobernó partes de Mesopotamia. Incluyó el reino de Hammurabi, considerada la edad dorada del período Babilónico Antiguo.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Verwijst naar de Oud-Babylonische periode van 1894 tot 1595 v. Chr., toen één dynastie over delen van Mesopotamië regeerde. Tot deze dynastie behoorde Hammurabi, wiens regeerperiode wordt beschouwd als de gouden eeuw van de Oud-Babylonische tijd.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052378/Winkler Prins Encyclopedie (1990)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指自西元前1894年至西元前1595年間，由某一王朝統治美索不達米亞部分地區的古巴比倫王朝時代。此王朝被認為是古巴比倫王朝的黃金時代，漢摩拉比（Hammurabi）國王即於此時期在位。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
